urls.title: Get Credit for Rare NFT's on ParaSpace
urls.description: ParaSpace will enable owners of rare or "grail" NFT's to access greater credit when used as collateral.

data.text:
These are our current estimates for grail trait boosts across the #BAYC, #MAYC, #BAKC, #Otherdeed, and #Azuki. These collections have cumulatively generated some of the highest volumes of any NFT collections. 

Learn more: https://t.co/h2BpfJRPaz https://t.co/uYpKuKunnV

Grail Traits on ParaSpace: We're looking at traits across top-tier NFT collections that have empirically gathered an average Floor Multiple sale price of at least 2x and have consistently garnered substantial premiums in sales against the collection’s floor price. https://t.co/6g2cgbB7e7
Top collections supported by @ParaSpace_NFT measured an average liquidity premium of ~8% discount in Floor Multiple between “Offer” and “Purchase” sales. https://t.co/DXFuz5THzD

Sharp spikes in accepted offers coincide w/ times of strong crypto coin and NFT market volatility.

- The liquidity premium is heavily correlated with market sentiment & dynamics.
- In times of strong market stress/turmoil, premiums for these grail traits fall.

NFT prices can be volatile, and a key factors is what we call a “liquidity premium”—how much of price are you willing to give up to accept a bid below your ask price?

Over time we see this can vary pretty significantly based on market conditions. https://t.co/3WAcI4qvAr

So-called “Grail” traits fetch significant premiums, particularly in top-tier NFT collections. As a P2Pool protocol, we’d like to give our users top-tier valuations for their rare NFTs while balancing the risk to lenders.
